songs.title: Mustang
songs.lyrics:
I ain't go no clues 'bout what I gotta be
And just fifteen seconds ago
I found my name
No need to turn me over
No need for drugs to help discover that
I finally found myself
Thank's to you
I think I'm not too bad for a white boy
I've always had the need to thank you
You used to drive a Mustang
You used to give us names
That was fifteen years ago
We've changed
No need to turn me over
No need for drugs
To help me discover that
I finally found my way
Thank's to you
I'm gonna tell you something
'Bout this white boy
I've always had this thing for you
